{"tid":1615651,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"【眾籌網絡文宣】721 831 101黑警槍殺人暴行推上國際","createTime":"2019-10-03T07:16:29.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-03T07:26:45.000Z","uid":191723,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"43daa7535dda594e09abbb1c3824339357e9b2e1","tid":1615651,"uid":191723,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T07:16:29.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">要將國殤日黑警以極近距離開槍打中五學生呢件事推到國際，目的要讓凝聚國際間支持聲音推翻警隊。就算有冇成立獨立調查委員會，呢隻差啲一槍打死人嘅杜狗都冇得留低<br />\n重申監警會冇撚用，搵隻狗查番狗等於左手查右手，所以一定要成立獨立調查委員會，如果唔係啲狗次次打完人都冇手尾跟，仲要一次比一次暴力今次連實彈都出埋。DLLMCH</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n如果你支持屌尻隻杜狗和推呢單野上國際請幫推上熱門及捐款。<br />\n<br />\n我冇能力保護嗰位中五學生，呢場運動應該係我哋大人出黎抗爭，我哋嘅錯就應該我哋自已去補救，冇理由要學生幫忙，仲要呢位學生被人告暴動罪，黑警一定要死全家<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KeCiVMR.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKeCiVMR.jpg&h=a8533ad0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><ins><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">宣傳目標對象</span></ins></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: brown;\">全香港人不論黃藍中立政見</span></strong><br />\n宣揚黑警一直以來暴行，我相信有好多上左年紀嘅人未必知黑警開槍打學生嘅事，我唔知黑警所謂嘅最低武力定義係咩，當年葉繼歡都係下半身中槍落網，今日黑警竟然對住一個學生心臟位置開槍。黑警死全家<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: brown;\">外國人</span></strong><br />\n希望爭取國際支持推翻淪為政治工具嘅垃圾警隊，重組為真‧香港人服務嘅警隊。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NQ3qAM6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNQ3qAM6.jpg&h=4a9c43ae&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">廣告宣傳內容</span></span></ins></strong><br />\n<br />\n黑警以謊言掩飾暴行，再將責任推向義士。<br />\n黑警選擇性執法，對義士就暴力鎮壓，對藍絲的施襲者卻加以保護、不斷縱容及高調放生。美其名維持社會安寧，實則是濫用過份暴力協助維穩政權，目的達致民眾禁聲的效果。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1gt2C0w.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1gt2C0w.jpg&h=ba8461b2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<ins><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">廣告宣傳平台</span></span></strong></ins><br />\n<br />\nGoogle 廣告 （圖像廣告）<br />\nYoutube 廣告 （不少於3分鐘廣告影片）<br />\nFacebook 廣告 （不少於3分鐘廣告影片）<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><ins>其他</ins></strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n預定廣告持續時間為1個月（視乎眾籌金額所定） <br />\n<br />\n三個平台廣告都會根據眾籌金額而調整廣告預算，務求讓更多人可以清楚了解黑警暴行，從而改變立場，支持推翻警隊。<br />\n<br />\n所有眾籌資金將用作文宣廣告費用，本團隊絕不會私取任何金錢，全部廣告費用都會清楚在Telegram channel和眾籌頁面公佈，每星期更新一次廣告費用支出，因此大家都能夠清楚了解所有費用去向。<br />\n<br />\n歡迎大家追蹤tg channel，所有有關反送中運動的資訊和廣告費用都會在此tg channel公佈，有問題想了解亦可以tg我。<br />\n<br />\n眾籌連結：<a href=\"https://gogetfunding.com/antielab/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgogetfunding.com%2Fantielab%2F&d=2%2FeNT3TbtuwIHwt2a%2FmQGMLrQrhaJullgCUoYOUuTa8%3D&h=679b63d6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://gogetfunding.com/antielab/</a><br />\nTelegram channel：<a href=\"https://t.me/AntiELABHongKong\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FAntiELABHongKong&d=2%2FeNT3TbtuwIHwt2a%2FmQGMLrQrhaJullgCUoYOUuTa8%3D&h=e177f815\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/AntiELABHongKong</a><br />\nTelegram：<a href=\"https://t.me/Anti_ELAB_HK\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FAnti_ELAB_HK&d=2%2FeNT3TbtuwIHwt2a%2FmQGMLrQrhaJullgCUoYOUuTa8%3D&h=f8b97a7a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/Anti_ELAB_HK</a>"},{"pid":"884ba6b82886ce3585d678cab6e4ad521788ab6c","tid":1615651,"uid":191723,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T07:16:42.000Z","msg":"自推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7b7d70235b9c5989e35b85c67b20dc112b2e3a39","tid":1615651,"uid":191723,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T07:16:52.000Z","msg":"自推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9c10e64896fbd7d75f6618ffba1b4584c5d32e92","tid":1615651,"uid":191723,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"repl